.TH LOA-COMPACT 1 "2026-03-15" "Library Of Alexandria" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
compact \- Toggle compact table mode
.SH SYNOPSIS
alexandria> compact
.br
alexandria> compact on
.br
alexandria> compact off
.br
alexandria> compact toggle
.br
alexandria> compact status
.SH DESCRIPTION
.TP
Controls whether list output uses full or compact table layout.
.TP
Compact mode shows fewer columns for faster scanning.
.SH EXAMPLES
.TP
alexandria> compact toggle
.TP
alexandria> list
.SH SEE ALSO
loa(1), loa-list(1)
.SH AUTHOR
Generated for the Library Of Alexandria project.
